{"tid":1888091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"古有關雲長捉棋刮骨療毒，今有小提琴家拉小提琴做腦手術","createTime":"2020-02-20T03:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T04:11:30.000Z","uid":230416,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"19aec4604e11cff61c3ed083fcad2ebd591f7b96","tid":1888091,"uid":230416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/4356792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F4356792&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=14efc941\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/4356792</a><br />\n<br />\n為保音樂才華 英國女子邊動腦部手術邊拉提琴<br />\n2020-02-19 23:07 中央社 / 倫敦19日綜合外電報導<br />\n英國女子特納在醫院動腦部腫瘤切除手術時，以小提琴拉奏奧地利作曲家馬勒和美國作曲家蓋希文創作的音樂，如此外科醫生就能保留她的演奏能力及她40年來對小提琴的熱愛。<br />\n<br />\n路透社報導，53歲的特納（Dagmar Turner）來自英國懷特島（Isle of Wight），先前曾擔任管理顧問。她在醫生為她手術切除大腦右額葉的腫瘤時，拉奏小提琴。右額葉接近大腦控制左手細微動作的區域。<br />\n<br />\n為防損及特納拉琴的功力，倫敦國王學院醫院（King's College Hospital）神經外科顧問醫師阿希甘（Keyoumars Ashkan）想到一個方法。手術團隊繪製特納腦部影像、打開頭骨，而後讓特納在醫生切除腫瘤時拉奏小提琴。<br />\n<br />\n外科醫生為特納切除腦部腫瘤時，特納拉奏馬勒（Gustav Mahler）創作的音樂、蓋希文（GeorgeGershwin）的爵士樂經典作品「夏日時光」（Summertime），以及西班牙創作歌手胡立歐（JulioIglesias）的歌曲。<br />\n<br />\n阿希甘說：「這是第一次有患者在動手術時演奏樂器。我們成功移除超過90%的腫瘤，包含所有疑似有侵略性活動的部位，同時保留她左手完整的功能。」<br />\n<br />\n特納感謝為她動手術的醫生。她說：「我對小提琴充滿熱情，我從10歲就開始拉小提琴。想到會喪失拉琴能力就令我感到心碎。」<br />\n<br />\n英國「電訊報」（Telegraph）報導，特納在動腦部腫瘤切除手術時拉小提琴，創下英國醫界首例。<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b878108b7a76f0efa2737fa84e4aee5bd2f067e","tid":1888091,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65459fc7bf413e2f9081403be15bf63fffdab7e","tid":1888091,"uid":67186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T03:59:38.000Z","msg":"做腦手術唔係靠呢啲畫下畫，對答去確保唔會切多咗"},{"pid":"e081ddb496b17388b79b8a04ff4071dba0afe0dc","tid":1888091,"uid":147721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:00:30.000Z","msg":"清醒開顱手術啫 講到新大陸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8079c054f5d8a4464e02f3a4a7b5f6189d1fbe69","tid":1888091,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/lZM2lqetUaiYLihMzsRIHL-Vjy993qBAjmIe9Jy70pWiENDVp4FufUMNZkqFG2kUocw2Z5UIpjsfU-BdJ3c_ZQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FlZM2lqetUaiYLihMzsRIHL-Vjy993qBAjmIe9Jy70pWiENDVp4FufUMNZkqFG2kUocw2Z5UIpjsfU-BdJ3c_ZQ&h=abbb1242&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b70191311143ea2efac49e1bed5feb9a1af7e3d7","tid":1888091,"uid":297672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T04:11:30.000Z","msg":"刮骨癲好多"}]}